# Cursor AI Rules

This project uses shared AI guidelines. Please read and follow the complete guidelines in:
- `docs/AI_GUIDELINES.md` - Complete architecture and development guidelines

Key points:
- Prefer Server Actions over API routes for mutations
- Use direct data fetching in Server Components over API routes
- Only create API endpoints when absolutely necessary (webhooks, cron jobs, external APIs)
- Follow the Next.js App Router best practices outlined in the guidelines
